thread.title: BRIEF-SI-TECH Information Technology to set up controlling unit Si-Tech GmBH & Teamshub GmBH in Germany

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-SI-TECH Information Technology to set up controlling unit Si-Tech GmBH & Teamshub GmBH in Germany

organizations.name: reuters) - si-tech information technology co ltd

text:
Feb 5 (Reuters) - SI-TECH Information Technology Co Ltd :
* Says it plans to set up tech subsidiary named Si-Tech GmBH & Teamshub GmBH in Germany with an individual for oversea market expansion
* The JV will be capitalized at 5.5 million yuan and the company will hold a 91 percent stake with investment of 5 million yuan
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/aiocrk
